OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMotor neurone disease:     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'False hope' given to Welsh
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpatients                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "False hope" has been given to people  
OL,6, with motor neurone disease (MND) in    
OL,7, Wales, according to the family of a man
OL,8, with the terminal illness.             
OL,10,FPatients have been told they can access
OL,11,Ftrials and support services in England,
OL,12,Fhelped by #50m in funding, as there is 
OL,13,Fno MND research centre in Cardiff.     
OL,15,FBut Bob Gledhill, 53, from Carmarthen, 
OL,16,Fsaid he was unable to get a referral.  
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said support was  
OL,19,Favailable for some to take part in     
OL,20,Ftrials outside of Wales.               
